_text = "Out of all the rooms in this house, this was my favourite. I call it the Basement. How original.\n\nThis space was everything to me. The whole basement was mine to host game nights in, halloween parties and sleepovers with friends. We would spend all nighters playing video games, watching movies and gorging on anything we found in the pantry. My dad would always surprise us with chips and pop if he knew I was having friends over.\n\nThese memories were so simple, but they remain a time where I could truly enjoy life without the responsibilities of being an adult. I miss how simple life was. I miss how my biggest worry was if my friend couldn't sleep over for the third night in a row.I didn't see how good I had it."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, BasementLeftMemory, BasementLeftMemory, false)
